  <h1>Chip Flavor Taste Test Analysis</h1>
  <p>For my 32nd birthday my family got together and did a massive chip taste test focused on unique or international varities. Everyone rated each chip on a scale of 0-100 for relative enjoyment and then scored them for how authentic the flavor match was. This activity was heavily inspired by Good Mythical Morning.</p>
  <p>Claude performed the following data analysis based on all 7 participants' individual ratings of 22 different chip flavors.</p>
  
