    </div>
    <div class="insight-box">
      <h3>Key Insights:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li class="list-item"><span class="key-point">Chamoy! (Kettle Brand)</span> was Dame's absolute favorite with a score of 95/100.</li>
        <li class="list-item">Dame's least favorite was <span class="key-point">Pizza Party (Trader Joe's)</span> with only 25/100.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  
